Found at 15 McNamara Drive, across from the Paradise Community Center and close proximity to Paradise Plaza, Walter Pennell Place offers a range of options for retail, office and professional service users. With various sizes available across three modern and bright floors, Walter Pennell Place offers the opportunity for your business to join an existing strong and diverse tenant mix-which includes bakery, pizza, fitness and office. Main floor units have direct access outside, ideal for retail or professional services. Units are ranging in size from 900 sf up to 3000 sf. All units are vanilla boxed and can be built to suit; dedicated HRV and electrical supply to all units.

Opportunity to own your own commercial building in Clarke’s Beach with a spectacular unobstructed view of the ocean. This 7000 sf building offers a large main floor space measures approximately 3600 sf and has public washrooms, large open retail/service/restaurant space, a smaller sales area and large backroom/production/manufacturing area. Upper level boast shard wood in 2 large open rooms plus bonus third room with plumbing hookup totaling 2050 sf. Attached warehouse/storage area off back of building adding 1100 sf to the building. Basement is not developed. A number of upgrade shave transpired over the past couple of years. Option available to lease entire building for $2200/month.
